---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Card from "@/components/Card.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="">
  <main
    class="min-h-[60vh] flex flex-col justify-center items-center mx-auto max-w-[calc(100%-2rem)] text-[rgb(var(--foreground))] text-lg leading-relaxed m-4 sm:m-4"
  >
    <h1 class="font-['DungGeunMo'] text-6xl mt-4 mb-8 sm:mb-16 text-center">
      <span class="">한줄코딩</span>
    </h1>
    <div>
      <p class="instructions">
        이 프로젝트는 <code>Astro.js</code> 로 만들어졌으며, 현재 <strong>지속적으로 작업 중</strong>인 상태 입니다.<br
        />
      </p>
      <ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
        <Card
          href="https://github.com/hanjulcoding/hanjulcoding"
          title="Repository"
          body="현재 작업 중인 이 사이트의 Repo"
        />
        <Card
          href="https://6lueparr0t.github.io"
          title="6lueparr0t's Home"
          body="개발자 홈페이지"
        />
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .instructions {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--foreground));
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .instructions code {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    border: 1px solid rgba(var(--foreground));
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
  }
  .link-card-grid {
    display: grid;
    /* grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(24ch, 1fr)); */
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 0;
  }
</style>
